GET {{baseUrl}}/vendors?page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Vendors (with search)
GET {{baseUrl}}/vendors?searchTerm=tech
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get specific Vendor by ID
# Replace with actual UUID from the vendors list
GET {{baseUrl}}/vendors/YOUR_VENDOR_UUID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Create Vendor
POST {{baseUrl}}/vendors
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
