################################################################################
# NOTES
################################################################################
#
# Token Expiration:
# - Access tokens typically expire in 1 hour
# - If you get 401 errors, repeat the token acquisition process
#
# Location Context:
# - Your token is associated with specific Logto Organizations (locations)
# - API calls are filtered by your current location
# - Use the location switcher in the UI to change locations
#
# Testing Different Users:
# - Sign out in browser (http://localhost:3004)
# - Repeat token acquisition with different user credentials
# - Or use Incognito/Private browsing mode
#
################################################################################
